	<ol class="commentlist">
			<li class="comment byuser comment-author-nantalith comment-author-is-site-member even thread-even depth-1 highlander-comment" id="comment-1366" >
		<div class="c-grav"><img alt='' src='https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/3fcc8a44f32974435a7d9fd5ce89161e?s=40&#038;d=identicon&#038;r=G' class='avatar avatar-40' height='40' width='40' /></div>
		<div class="c-body">
			<div class="c-head">
				<a href='http://nantalith.wordpress.com/' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>nantalith</a> <span class="c-permalink"><a href="https://micfic.wordpress.com/2011/03/06/blue-genes/#comment-1366">permalink</a></span>
			</div>
						<p>Interesting.  I first thought he was going to save the world from what his daughter could, or rather, will become.  But then I had another thought.  Tom also has parents, what if both his parents had&#8230;  Is he acting out urges he has long held in check or saving his daughter from what she will become?</p>
						<div class="reply">
				<a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='https://micfic.wordpress.com/2011/03/06/blue-genes/?replytocom=1366#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm( "comment-1366", "1366", "respond", "791" )' aria-label='Reply to nantalith'>Reply</a>			</div>
